  <brief_title>Arterial Calcifications in Nocturnal Hemodialysis and Renal Transplantation Versus Conventional Dialysis</brief_title>
  <acronym>NOCTX</acronym>
  <official_title>Is Progression of Arteriosclerosis in ESRD Patients Inhibited by Nocturnal Hemodialysis or Renal Transplantation?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
